overview: July 13th, 2008 :: For one day only, Senior Official Bryce Remsburg is the acting Director of Fun! Mike Quackenbush looks for revenge against Shane Storm following his betrayal. Brodie Lee and Claudio Castagnoli look to settle their differences in a No Disqualification match! Both the Young Lions Cup and los Campeonatos de Parejas are contested on this loaded card. Matches featured:  1. Eddie Kingston vs Lince Dorado  2. Jimmy Olsen vs Ultimo Breakfast  3. Osirian Portal , F.I.S.T. vs The Colony , Super Smash Brothers  4. Chuck Taylor vs Incognito  5. Shane Storm vs Mike Quackenbush  6. Young Lions Cup Match Vin Gerard vs Fire Ant  7. UltraMantis Black vs Tim Donst  8. No Disqualification Match Brodie Lee vs Claudio Castagnoli  9. Campeonatos de Parejas Match The Fabulous Two vs Incoherence.
title: Chikara Tragedy And Triumph
